table.whereclause: (CLASSIFICATIONID IN (SELECT CLASSIFICATIONID FROM CLASSSTRUCTURE WHERE USEWITHLOCATIONS = 1))
(CLASSIFICATIONID IN (SELECT DISTINCT LBL_CLASSID FROM PM WHERE LBL_CLASSID IS NOT NULL))
(CLASSIFICATIONID IN (SELECT DISTINCT LBL_CLASSID FROM JOBPLAN WHERE LBL_CLASSID IS NOT NULL))
entityname in (select tablename from maxtable where isaudittable = 1)
runtype in( select value from synonymdomain where synonymdomain.maxvalue in ('BIRT') and synonymdomain.domainid in ('REPORTTYPES') )
itemnum in( select distinct itemnum from toolinv)
name in (select name from skdproject where usewith='RLASSIGN' and (createby=:USER or (ispublic=1)))
classstructureid in (select a.classstructureid from classstructure a where a.parent IN (SELECT b.CLASSSTRUCTUREID FROM CLASSSTRUCTURE b WHERE b.classificationid='FAC-WPC'))
